# Privacy Policy

Last Updated: 03-OCT-2023

This Privacy Policy is intended to inform you about the collection, use, and disclosure of personal information when you use our Android application ("Amazing PDF Converter"). We respect your privacy and are committed to safeguarding your personal information. This Policy explains how we handle your data and outlines your rights concerning your data.

1. Information We Don't Collect

We want to assure you that our App does not collect, store, or transmit any personal information or data. We do not collect the following types of information:

a. Personal Information: We do not collect your name, email address, phone number, or any other personal identifier.

b. Location Information: Our App does not access or track your location.

c. Device Information: We do not gather information about your device, including device type, operating system, or unique device identifiers.

d. Usage Information: We do not collect information about how you use the App, such as which features you access or how often you use it.

e. Contacts: We do not access your contacts or address book.

2. Permissions We Require

a. Our App only requests or require camera and storage permissions, in order to allow users to access camera and storage to selecte files for conversion process.

3. Analytics and Third-Party Services

We do not use any third-party analytics or tracking services that might collect data about your usage of the App. Additionally, we do not integrate any third-party services or SDKs that would collect personal information.


4. Security

While we do not collect any personal information, we are committed to protecting any data you provide voluntarily or any data generated while using the App. We use industry-standard security measures to safeguard this data.

5. Children's Privacy

Our App is not directed at children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect any personal information from such individuals. If you are a parent or guardian and believe that your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us so that we can delete it.

6. Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time, primarily to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. The updated Privacy Policy will be posted on this page, and the date of the latest revision will be displayed at the top.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions, concerns, or requests related to your privacy or this Privacy Policy, please contact us at aizaz319@gmail.com.

By using our App, you consent to this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with the terms of this Policy, please do not use our App.
